com.rdio.android.api

Interface RdioApiCallback


  • public interface RdioApiCallback
    A callback listener for Rdio.apiCall() requests to the web service API.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void onApiFailure(java.lang.String methodName, java.lang.Exception e)

      Called if the API call succeeds.

    • Method Detail

      • onApiFailure

        void onApiFailure(java.lang.String methodName,
                java.lang.Exception e)
        Called if the API call fails (results in an HTTP error code != 200)
        Parameters:
        methodName - Name of the method that failed
        e - If an exception is generated, then it will be passed here

      • onApiSuccess

        void onApiSuccess(org.json.JSONObject result)
        Called if the API call succeeds. The JSONObject returned by the API call will be passed here.
        Parameters:
        result - See http://www.rdio.com/developers/docs/web-service/index/
